summary: this files replace races for lotr races
descriptionHtml:
the first ALPHA.esp replace the beast races for dwarfs and hobbits, the second replace vanilla elves for lotr elves and magic guys for elders, also the orc race now are just males.
the third alpha replace falmers for dwarven machines, giants for centurions and snow cats for ice wraiths. have fun.
this mod is complement for any lotr compilation. maybe need downguard. sorry for the bad english. thanks to Blackthorrn for Erebor mod.
